data.description: 10.77 acres of pure country awaiting you in SE Lamar county on county road corner! 2018 model Legacy Mobile home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, open living-dining-kitchen combination. The front of the home faces the north for a great view of the larger pond and pasture. 20x20 deck allows the opportunity to enjoy the evening sunsets and view of the property.  Large concrete pad to the west makes for a nice open patio. Property is completely fenced, cross-fenced for easy cattle or horse operation.  2 nice ponds located on north and south sections of land. Older barn has electricity and country water.  Conex container has electricity.  Carport covers can double as storage area. Easy access to property with county road frontage on two sides.  Prairiland ISD.  Washer, dryer and refrigerator conveys at closing.
